Dear Parent_C,

Thank you for your message and for staying engaged with the process.

1) Yes—if/when we determine that none of the higher‑priority families on our list (Parent_D, Parent_E, Parent_A, Parent_B) will take the remaining place, we will move to the next available family and proactively contact you in that same round to invite an immediate formal [APPLY] so we can make a prompt, same‑round decision.

2) To be ready to complete enrollment the same day, it would be helpful to have the following prepared (where applicable):
- Child/parent identification and contact details;
- Any required medical/allergy information and immunisation/health records;
- Emergency contacts and authorised pick‑up list;
- Preferred start date and any settling‑in availability;
- Readiness to pay any standard deposit/fees promptly upon offer (timing and method can be confirmed at that point).

Please note that while we will contact you immediately if the seat is released to the next family, we cannot commit to a specific round when that will occur.

Sincerely,
Nursery_C Admissions

[TALK]
